== Parents death? ==

"He was the fourth of five children of Countess Mariya Tolstaya, née Raevskaya. Tolstoy's parents died when he was young, so he and his siblings were brought up by relatives"
Mariya Volkonskaya died August 10, 1863. Tolstoy would of been 34 years old.
[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mariya_Volkonskaya]
Never mind. The Mariya Volkonskaya page has removed the info about Tolstoy.

