== Famous quotes ==

The famous quotes from Tolstoy are:
1. Honesty
2. Good books
3. Accompanying nature and art
4. Good works

To read more about the quotes, go to following website : http://www.brainyquote.com/quotes/authors/l/leo_tolstoy.html

